name: Doumu
description:
The digital painting “Doumu” was created in 2011, on a MacBook pro with photoshop. Doumu is the Lady Mother of the Chariot, represented in Taoism to be the feminine aspect of the cosmic God of Heaven. 

We have been designers since 2010 and our only webspace channel of communication was through social media, (Instagram, Facebook). Although these channels are limited, they have helped us grow in the past, but the future on these platforms is obsolete as restrictions on creativity are expanding. 

We are transiting into the digital space, the remaining time of the physical world is decreasing. We exist in a time of transition, the trajectory of cryptocurrency and NFT is heading towards the foreseeable future, it is an exciting opportunity to be able to create freely and be supported. We are jumping in with curiosity, skepticism, and respect for real creators and artists.
